provisions.content:
context,___
(a)        “export” means taking to any place outside Pakistan by any means;
(b)        “prescribed” means prescribed by rules made under this Ordinacne;
(c)        “sugar” does not include khandsari and Palmyra sugar;
(d)        “sugar-cane” means the plant saccharum officinarum which is commonly
known as the sugar-cane and from which sugar is obtained.
